ed back to correct error. Example: cruise control. Robust to disturbances but can oscillate if not designed carefully."]}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","h3","h3-1",{"children":"1.2 State-Space Representation"}],"\n",["$","p","p-5",{"children":"The most general linear system representation:"}],"\n",["$","p","p-6",{"children":"\\[\\dot{x}(t) = Ax(t) + Bu(t)\\]\n\\[y(t) = Cx(t) + Du(t)\\]"}],"\n",["$","p","p-7",{"children":"where:"}],"\n",["$","ul","ul-2",{"children":["\n",["$","li","li-0",{"children":"\\(x \\in \\mathbb{R}^n\\) — state vector (internal system memory)"}],"\n",["$","li","li-1",{"children":"\\(u \\in \\mathbb{R}^m\\) — control input vector"}],"\n",["$","li","li-2",{"children":"\\(y \\in \\mathbb{R}^p\\) — measured output vector"}],"\n",["$","li","li-3",{"children":"\\(A \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n \\times n}\\) — system matrix (dynamics)"}],"\n",["$","li","li-4",{"children":"\\(B \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n \\times m}\\) — input matrix"}],"\n",["$","li","li-5",{"children":"\\(C \\in \\mathbb{R}^{p \\times n}\\) — output matrix"}],"\n",["$","li","li-6",{"children":"\\(D \\in \\mathbb{R}^{p \\times m}\\) — feedthrough matrix"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","p","p-8",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Discrete-time version"}]," (for digital controllers with sampling period \\(T_s\\)):"]}],"\n",["$","p","p-9",{"children":"\\[x[k+1] = A_d x[k] + B_d u[k]\\]\n\\[y[k] = Cx[k] + Du[k]\\]"}],"\n",["$","p","p-10",{"children":"where \\(A_d = e^{AT_s}\\), \\(B_d = \\int_0^{T_s} e^{A\\tau} B d\\tau\\). Digital control requires sampling fast enough to capture system dynamics (Shannon-Nyquist: \\(f_s > 2 f_{max}\\))."}],"\n",["$","h3","h3-2",{"children":"1.3 Transfer Function (Laplace Domain)"}],"\n",["$","p","p-11",{"children":"For linear time-invariant systems, the transfer function:"}],"\n",["$","p","p-12",{"children":"\\[G(s) = \\frac{Y(s)}{U(s)} = C(sI - A)^{-1}B + D\\]"}],"\n",["$","p","p-13",{"children":"captures input-output relationships in the frequency domain. Key tools:"}],"\n",